## Shared team learnings

The directory `.claude/agent-context/` accumulates team knowledge — module gotchas, infrastructure quirks, architecture rules — captured during real work. Lead injects relevant entries into subagent prompts so the same lessons aren't relearned every session.

Check `.claude/agent-context/` for entries relevant to whatever you're touching:

```bash
ls .claude/agent-context/
```

These files are committed to git so all team members benefit. Personal notes live in `.claude/agent-memory-local/lead/` (gitignored).

